quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,Kumpele chipaka kusonganganya (ya duniya mwampikisano kuleka ganisya ya Akhera)
  102,2,Mpaka nkwikanila kwaula ku malembe (n'di m'bwile)
  102,3,Ngwamba! Chinchiika kumanyilila
  102,4,Soni ngwamba! Chinchiika kumanyilila
  102,5,Ngwamba! Ingaŵe mwamanyililaga umanyilisi usyesyene (nga nganin'jijilikaga ni ya duniya)
  102,6,Chisimu chene chinkauone Moto Waukali
  102,7,Soni chinkauone kusyene ni liso lyakusimichisya
  102,8,Soni lyele lisikulyo tinkawusyidwe kusyene ya chindimba (chaŵampele pa duniya)